   "source": [
    "## Обучение"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "В данном разделе обучим три модели на основе TF-IDF. Для оценки метрики качества будем использовать F1."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 13,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "RANDOM_STATE = 42\n",
    "X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(\n",
    "    data['text'],\n",
    "    data['toxic'],\n",
    "    test_size=0.2,\n",
    "    random_state=RANDOM_STATE,\n",
    "    stratify=data['toxic']\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "pipeline = Pipeline([\n",
    "    ('tfidf', TfidfVectorizer(\n",
    "        ngram_range=(1, 2),\n",
    "        max_df=0.9,\n",
    "        min_df=3\n",
    "    )),\n",
    "    ('model', LogisticRegression(\n",
    "        max_iter=1000,\n",
    "        class_weight='balanced',\n",
    "        random_state=RANDOM_STATE\n",
    "    ))\n",
    "])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "cv_scores = cross_val_score(\n",
    "    pipeline,\n",
    "    data['text'],\n",
    "    data['toxic'],\n",
    "    cv=3,\n",
    "    scoring='f1',\n",
    "    n_jobs=-1\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
